+------------------------------+
|  Kubernetes API Server       |  ← Talks to etcd (cluster state)
+------------------------------+
            ▲
            | Watches pod assignments
            ▼
+------------------------------+
|  Kubelet (Node Controller)   |  ← Watches API Server
+------------------------------+
            ▲
            | Talks to CRI (Container Runtime Interface)
            ▼
+------------------------------+
|  Container Runtime (containerd, CRI-O) |  ← Starts & manages containers
+------------------------------+
            ▲
            | Runs & monitors containers
            ▼
+------------------------------+
|  Running Containers          |  ← Actual state
+------------------------------+

